<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>śākābdē śaśiratnabhānugaṇutē caitrē sitē cāṣṭamī
<lb n="2" break="no"/>puṇyāhē haricaṁdanō ravikulaśrīrāmadēvātmajaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> khā 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>rīpaṁcakasaṁmitāṁ jalabhuvaṁ tōrāmusīmasthitāṁ
<lb n="4"/>prādātkūrmmapurādhipāya sakaḷābhīṣṭārtthasidy£ai
<lb n="5"/>stiraṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> koṟapamagrāme saggrāmāraṇyaṁ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> madīyyaṁ bhā
<lb n="6" break="no"/>gakṣētraṁca <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrīkamaṭhādipāya dattamācaṁdratārakaṁ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
<lb n="7"/>Atra vinayōgaḥ prasdhaṣaṭkamōdanaṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> nivēditaṁ khaṁḍapānīyaṁ
<lb n="8"/>kalaśaṁ mudgaṁ ca Ētanmadhyē puṣpamālādānārtthaṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> purāyi
<lb n="9" break="no"/>naṭṭuvaputrasya prōlunaṭṭavasya prasthadvayaṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> tasyaiva vētanaṁ
<lb n="10"/>ciṁhnukadaśakaṁ tasyānujāyāḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Akkāsānyāḥ śayyābhōgasa
<lb n="11" break="no"/>mayē cāmaradhāraṇāya prasthadvayaṁ khaṁḍapānīyyaṁ mu
<lb n="12" break="no"/>dgaṁca tasyaiva Ētadanusaṁddhānārtthaṁ prasthadvayaṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Ī dattamu
<lb n="13" break="no"/>tirupati śrīvaiṣṇavarakṣa <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrīśrīśrī<note n="457-1">Below this inscription are engraved two goads on a pedestal.</note>
</p>

